      "source": [
        "# Garbage Image Classification — CNN dari Nol (Diperbaiki)\n",
        "\n",
        "Notebook ini melatih **CNN dari nol** (tanpa pretrained ImageNet) untuk 6 kelas:\n",
        "**cardboard, glass, metal, paper, plastic, trash**\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Perbandingan:** Bandingkan dengan MobileNetV2 di folder `practice 9`. Notebook ini fokus **menyempurnakan CNN scratch** tanpa transfer learning.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Kelas lemah yang perlu diperbaiki:** metal, plastic (plastik bening), trash/organik (OOD)\n",
        "\n",
        "**Strategi penyempurnaan (urutan prioritas):**\n",
        "1. **Tambah foto** ke folder `metal/` dan `plastic/` (paling efektif)\n",
        "2. **Focal Loss** + bobot kelas lebih tinggi untuk metal/plastic\n",
        "3. **Confusion matrix** — lihat kelas mana yang sering tertukar\n",
        "4. **TTA** saat inference — rata-rata prediksi beberapa variasi gambar\n",
        "5. Ulangi training → evaluasi → tambah data lagi"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 1. Import Library"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 1,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "TensorFlow version: 2.18.0\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import tensorflow as tf\n",
        "from sklearn.utils import class_weight\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, confusion_matrix\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "from tensorflow.keras.preprocessing.image import ImageDataGenerator\n",
        "from tensorflow.keras.models import Sequential\n",
        "from tensorflow.keras.layers import (\n",
        "    Conv2D, MaxPooling2D, BatchNormalization,\n",
        "    GlobalAveragePooling2D, Dropout, Dense\n",
        ")\n",
        "from tensorflow.keras.regularizers import l2\n",
        "from tensorflow.keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping, ReduceLROnPlateau, ModelCheckpoint\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "def categorical_focal_loss(gamma=2.0):\n",
        "    \"\"\"Fokus belajar pada contoh sulit (metal/plastic) — mengurangi dominasi cardboard yang mudah.\"\"\"\n",
        "    def loss(y_true, y_pred):\n",
        "        y_pred = tf.clip_by_value(y_pred, 1e-7, 1.0 - 1e-7)\n",
        "        cross_entropy = -y_true * tf.math.log(y_pred)\n",
        "        focal_weight = tf.pow(1.0 - y_pred, gamma)\n",
        "        return tf.reduce_mean(tf.reduce_sum(focal_weight * cross_entropy, axis=-1))\n",
        "    return loss\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"TensorFlow version: {tf.__version__}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 2. Konfigurasi Dataset & Preprocessing\n",
        "\n",
        "Menggunakan `ImageDataGenerator` dengan augmentasi agresif (Cheatsheet 7.1.1) dan `rescale=1./255` untuk CNN dari nol."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 2,
      "metadata": {},
